{"tid":658372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川震將屆滿10週年 中國定為「感恩日」","createTime":"2018-05-09T02:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T03:29:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a2468a8ace1999160d707433b6dc5fa0f8c05878","tid":658372,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:19:41.000Z","msg":"綜合媒體報導，2008年5月12日，四川省汶川縣發生芮氏規模8.2強震，造成6萬8712人死亡、1萬7921人失蹤，光是在震央汶川縣映秀鎮，全鎮過萬居民半數死亡或失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n如今川震將屆滿10週年，中國官媒《新華社》7日指出，汶川縣政府已宣佈5月12日定為感恩日，藉此「銘記傷痛、更銘記湧泉之恩」。映秀鎮中灘堡村支部書記楊雲兵說，「全國大愛匯聚這裡才有了映秀的今天，我們不能忘記」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2419356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2419356&d=VxHlKThWSdpvBcndEwljIk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f4b4015d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2419356&h=e54f8422\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2419356</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d668de23ab1bbe4fbec42613c6b94def19697ecd","tid":658372,"uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/111520_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F111520_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=381c617d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2a6cc66c8fd561f24efb8cd313fb299f522210c","tid":658372,"uid":33868,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"白事變紅事"},{"pid":"11c52bda1f236af3244ebd51ff8ec4ea57213c3c","tid":658372,"uid":53666,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n<br />\n南京大清洗感恩日丫，笨"},{"pid":"246a81f5e8f47fb6181243fc6e54111ee1f763