":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"咁震多幾次啦"},{"pid":"60e54522217462298b892a4d5ce9fd3bb36e7895","tid":658372,"uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"非洲有事我都會同情 <br />\n<br />\n但我就係唔同情中國 <br />\n<br />\n中國人係香港人的敵人 <br />\n<br />\n你話我冇同情心, 唔識分國黨都好 <br />\n<br />\n中國人逼害緊香港人係事實 <br />\n<br />\n我成日都話共產黨同帝制冇分別, <br />\n<br />\n一日keep住中國文化, 一日就會有共產黨 <br />\n<br />\n係中國人自己一手造成今日的極權, <br />\n<br />\n係中國人簡接/直接害死香港 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔會同情敵人, <br />\n<br />\n係我黑心? <br />\n<br />\n當D蝗民係咁搶香港福利, <br />\n<br />\n推高物價 <br />\n<br />\n控制香港政府 <br />\n<br />\n打壓言論自由 <br />\n<br />\n打壓法治 <br />\n<br />\n我再黑心都未夠中國人黑心 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔會收返我之前講過的野"},{"pid":"b66625a6f0fba594f967f4d2d002cbea613f51f2","tid":658372,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"當年班蝗蟲都一直侵略緊香港架啦 <br />\n個時係高登仲有唔少人話,我捐100蚊,就算得10蚊落到災民手上,都會捐,起碼幫到佢地 <br />\n真係天真,捐100蚊,隨時100蚊都落左格啦 <br />\n貼錢俾人落黎香港搶名牌搶私樓搶你條女仲話幫你添生活 <br />\n連港台節目都有訪問災民,個災民話無收到香港人捐助,話香港人識做既話要顯示出誠意$來 <br />\n貪官災民都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ,全部都非我族類 <br />\n<br />\n從來唔後悔當年係高登叫人唔好捐錢"},{"pid":"9ebf95ab6c195f84cbd147e300ee4209a26712bd","tid":658372,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"講開呢d我又想分享下 <br />\n最近我個有同事，話有個有錢朋友係中國山區起學校 <br />\n出左60萬，佢就係呢面公司籌期，會有善款收據 <br />\n問到我果時， <br />\n我話：錢我唔會捐 不過你地真係起到， <br />\n起完既話我捐1000支鉛筆or其他文具比你果面地址啦 <br />\n你比到地址我既話 <br />\n<br />\n佢就話：咁呀....我問下個朋友先 <br />\n之後就無左下文同無咩點理我 <br />\n<br />\n我係咪好衰呢 <br />\n<br />\n非洲果d助養我好樂意做"},{"pid":"ef3ae26473da17a7d8eb4689f042bf0250d888eb","tid":658372,"uid":55555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"AEON感謝日咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOn99"},{"pid":"22fabf31081e7ea9e1f985c6c47fe858ffbecdb0","tid":658372,"uid":115306,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"淘寶又多一日黎推銷假野<br />\n川震生環者專享7.2級地震折扣"},{"pid":"64201530d672accc3bc8f150e6e4998e1a27493a","tid":658372,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246a81f5e8f47fb6181243fc6e54111ee1f7633a","tid":658372,"uid":63853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"感恩天賜地震?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"梗係，唔係有天災的話，邊有咁多水 cap"},{"pid":"9e66bd5c304a435e2286771640277947117664db","tid":658372,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9affc4aefdd3b50bba382f4116279f4ded145ff6","tid":658372,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"睇錯川普"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"1fde198e9d04d9aa06f661f5963efed3605f10da","tid":658372,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"支國真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103d4721ac1c69b5fce914a87d78b3548f9579fe","tid":658372,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"咁我希望多啲感恩日,最好全個支那每個省最個縣每條村都用"},{"pid":"66e100c8b669f742e47718d87c2893a546f0b86f","tid":658372,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"咁我希望多啲感恩日,最好全個支那每個省最個縣每條村都<del>用</del>有"},{"pid":"0ea250b473164c56c1a227bce02ce5ce76347243","tid":658372,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d668de23ab1bbe4fbec42613c6b94def19697ecd","tid":658372,"uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.n