ji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247f722cae7d4cd11162be1a0fb50dfbf6116122","tid":658372,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T19:35:28.000Z","msg":"華北地震帶係時候要震一獲勁啦<br />\n好耐無震，一震就會震到仆街<br />\n我估2022前"},{"pid":"f7ef302fba2a6e76c76a4336d0e9632cbfc83470","tid":658372,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9935dad5039ee5225da7e27e75dc0f59c612923e","tid":658372,"uid":104443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感謝日本侵華！當年國軍喺前面同日軍打仗，共匪喺國軍後面放火！不打日軍，專殺國軍！抗戰勝利之後，趁國軍力量大減之際，一舉向中華民國展開毀滅性打擊！奪得大陸江山！如果冇日本侵華，就沒有黨！更沒有新中國！我地必須要感謝日本侵華！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T19:38:29.000Z","msg":"殺，殺到爛臭閪解放軍<br />\n電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1840631a08215fcd7647a95824aa71220287b066","tid":658372,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:03:24.000Z","msg":"前四川貪官：梗係要大事慶祝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314a194a4960cfefcdd651e526a51a13374c8adc","tid":658372,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:04:21.000Z","msg":"淘佬感謝日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a69f7cf8b4e937eb7d69d72d010ba7fca2f632","tid":658372,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00cfd00d12ba9788e3eff56bd169a9e15a720f6","tid":658372,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"國恥日就差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"你的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7872bd09c32592b6774ece8bd4f1e667af26e567","tid":658372,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64201530d672accc3bc8f150e6e4998e1a27493a","tid":658372,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"